sentences.english: You should also embed usability engineers on the project team.
sentences.chinese: 您還應該在項目團隊中安插可用性工程師。

sentences.english: When the plants could be seen having just one drink, all the subjects drank similar amounts.
sentences.chinese: 當安插者剛喝一杯的時候，所有人也都喝一杯的分量。

sentences.english: The questions come at strategic points in your flow.
sentences.chinese: 你需要把這些問題安插在故事的戰略要點處。

sentences.english: And then, moreover, you it was who placed me here.
sentences.chinese: 並且是您把我安插在這兒的。

sentences.english: The researchers designed a malicious app for the iPhone 4.
sentences.chinese: 研究人員在蘋果4代裏安插了一個惡意應用程序。

sentences.english: I am always glad to get a young person well placed out.
sentences.chinese: 我一貫喜歡讓一個年輕人得到很好的安插。

sentences.english: Handle railcar order orders and car placement tracking.
sentences.chinese: 處理機車爲了訂單和汽車安插跟蹤。

sentences.english: It is the spy seated in the central stronghold of the ego.
sentences.chinese: 它是安插在自我的中心堡壘中的暗探。

sentences.english: The police had planted a spy in the gang.
sentences.chinese: 警方在那團伙中安插了一名坐探。

sentences.english: I will try to sandwich the meeting in some time after lunch.
sentences.chinese: 我會設法將會議安插在午餐後的某個時間。

sentences.english: At this point the writer puts in [inserts] a flashback.
sentences.chinese: 作者在這裏安插了一段倒敘。

sentences.english: Spacers were also used to give a little breathing space to the radio buttons.
sentences.chinese: 間距器還可用於在單選按鈕之間安插一點距離。

sentences.english: With Ma Sha's help, Anping is appointed to be the deputy general manager of Universal hotel.
sentences.chinese: 馬沙把安平安插在聯合飯店當副總經理，以監視志忠。

sentences.english: Used to be , if spies wanted to eavesdrop, they planted a bug.
sentences.chinese: 在以前，如果想要竊聽他人，需要安插一個竊聽器。
